{"tid":1447672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今個星期搵日全民三罷 出街做文宣針對武警惡行","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:12.000Z","uid":25951,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc5f3f28710594bc9d6ce6536073e4880c9ca43","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:07:08.000Z","msg":"真心想問聽日係咪如常準時返工? 今日發生既事個個都嬲撚到仆街, 正常人都唔會有心情工作<br />\n<br />\n我知急call聽日罷工會太趕, 如果星期二呢? <span style=\"color: red;\">今次罷工唔係再集會啦, 係全世界print文宣出街派比街坊啊!!</span><br />\n<br />\n真係有好多人唔知今日d警察咁撚癲, 扮示威者、扮記者、插贓嫁禍、武警滲透、非禮女士......<br />\n呢個情況仲嚴重過612, 可以話係成個運動最黑暗既一日, 我地今日失去左幾多個義士? 數都未數得清就返工? 跟住下個禮拜六日又loop?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地宜家要做既野係宣傳黑警暴行, 瘋狂提返721元朗警黑勾結、恐怖襲擊</span></span><br />\nAirdrop既功效有限, 收到果插贓嫁禍個織圖咁撚細佢可以睇都唔睇就decline, 同埋好多時accept既可能都係自己友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最有效既係print晒d紙出黎貼街招+塞比人+主動講發生咩事</strong><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同意搵日罷工做文宣既麻煩推推post<br />\n唔同意就由佢啦<br />\nPS 歡迎勇武手足有其他plan, 呢個post係focus係文宣方面<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復白港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"cf58ef4af16e789f77403eb8bb7430790662bfe6","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:09:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6054d674a0280fee66b2a3795f9a310cd1708a13","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:06.000Z","msg":"文宣"},{"pid":"fc8d794b3829ff819c9b54011a5ac494f9951323","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:21.000Z","msg":"721 元朗恐襲"},{"pid":"b0ec252b0b1befa1b1f0b4f18de5573dbfac2233","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"721 元朗恐襲"},{"pid":"a55c1d3677cca2b5ec02aebd66b55fdd1ec2629f","tid":1447672,"uid":279650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:34.000Z","msg":"同意今星期內要有罷工及大遊行<br />\n<br />\n不要說推，請推以下<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內，極近距離開鎗<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n<br />\n文宣/民間記者會！！！！"},{"pid":"0f0289068844bbbb552abfaffd9981a3e676c306","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:41.000Z","msg":"721 元朗恐襲"},{"pid":"ac1d96637d258dda3fe2c5efa0105dba622b8177","tid":1447672,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvexDu8.jpg&h=6025e5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQpuBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQpuBP.jpg&h=bdc91acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Product should only be used outdoors. <br />\n<br />\nDo not fire directly at personnel</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者會上話會跟足廠商指引而無必要親身試彈，宜家冇跟指引就有必要親身試啦？</span><br />\n<br />\n間廠叫NonLethal Technology, 有冇人去提醒下間廠再培訓垃圾狗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2F&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=001dc6ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/</a>"},{"pid":"13d6b934cc12bed817d2c7220344d8144e275df1","tid":1447672,"uid":24265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仲唔孝敬班警察屋企人仲等乜呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.