By":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲第23日<br />\n警黑合作, 警署落閘, 999唔通<br />\n無人落charge <br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6. 警渣在一米距離內對示威者頭部連開數槍，等同謀殺。"},{"pid":"17c06725f1b46ba18920f9f0cfb58ac1a6592252","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"721 元朗恐襲<br />\n812 武警突襲"},{"pid":"d6a30a13915f16e5fb2a1f2494b5ecb4e50ecb9d","tid":1447672,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>明天宣布後天實行<br />\n<br />\n打鐵趁熱</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8a2805e4659179efdd93750b49364541492c85f9","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"9e708f7d17df2c94fa1aa1c04b1efb35fcc411b2","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"建議後日三罷"},{"pid":"6a0409c95da18321ce6093d0b3ad5cdd4cba8eae","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"星期二罷工做文宣"},{"pid":"5364b50751573cb7ff6e55321f8256a140b14296","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"272a270f6b04c90a47439f32d1df31581fdd20c4","tid":1447672,"uid":114501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"聽日罷"},{"pid":"f96de42fd764a4155a0e9c7fbd7a6f507f9e4a63","tid":1447672,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"文宣"},{"pid":"a6f35fc71d0cdb0d771bdf2956c138a6e3720244","tid":1447672,"uid":34630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:42.000Z","msg":"太急了"},{"pid":"6